{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, two hand-crafted features, including texture and shape-based features, were extracted from the input images, and principal component analysis was used for the best feature selection.",
    "These features were serially merged, and then feature selection was performed using the whale optimisation approach (WOA) and supplied to support vector machine, K-nearest neighbour, and wide neural network (WNN) classifiers.",
    "The performance of the proposed method was evaluated on X-ray radiographs of the elbow.",
    "The model obtained an accuracy of 97.1% with a kappa score of 94.3%.",
    "Manoila, C. et al."
  ]
}